<section class="vision-mission-section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="vm-grid">

      <!-- Image -->
      <div class="vm-image">
        <img src="/img/vision-mission.png" alt="Blossom World Faculty & Campus">
        <div class="vm-overlay"></div>
      </div>

      <!-- Content -->
      <div class="vm-content">
        <h2>Vision & Mission</h2>

        <div class="vm-card">
          <h4>Our Vision</h4>
          <p>
            A firm foundation along with a secure and assured future is promised under the roof of Blossom World Senior Secondary School. To set a path this is well catered and well-garnered. We take care of every passing minute of our students and make use of it in the most efficient way to turn it around for them in success, be it national or global. It is the vision of Blossom World Senior Secondary School to help give vision to our students at the right time in life; to exemplify excellence and leadership in the vast arena of Education.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="vm-card">
          <h4>Our Mission</h4>
          <p>
            Our mission is to serve society through excellence in education. We always aim to define, and continually refine, the absolute standard of excellence in the area of academics through the quality education, efficiency of our methodologies and systems, truthfulness towards parents, society and the nation.We are determined to instill positive attitudes, values, and vision that will prepare them for lifetime to fulfil their chosen carriers. 
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>


